title: Pumpkin walnut cookies
ingredients: ['55g margarine', '180ml vegetable oil', '200g caster sugar', '1 egg, beaten', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '250g pumpkin puree', '375g plain flour', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '100g walnuts']
